Version 0.1

- Added FlagsModifier providing the functionality to modify DNS and EDNS
  header flags (AA, TC, RD, RA, AD, CD, DO)

- Added configuration framework. Configuration is stored in INI file with
  main [Proxy] section and then sections for each configured modifier

- Added framework for creating new modifiers. New modifiers need to extend
  BaseModifier class and provide the _options_dict dictionary containing
  the default configuration. Also CONFIG_SECTION_NAME has to be provided
  with name of the configuration section (this is the same as name of the
  modifier in Modifiers= option od [Proxy] section.
